	else
		div.container
			div.row
				div.col-mid-12(style="font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif; margin-left: 15px")
					h2 KIVA Impact Calculator is a web application that assesses the degree of social impact created by KIVA loans by combining publicly available sources
					h2 Our sources include United Nations' Human Development Index and Quandl.
					h2 We combine the quantitative needs of the community with the actions of the lending community to infer the magnitude of the impact.
